      "text": "IS - X",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Re Bureau Bulletins No. 57 dated 10/1/47, and No.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "38 dated 3/25/49, entitled \"FLYING DISCS.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Enclosed are copies of an article entitled \"Armed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Forces - Focus on UFO\", which was published in the This World",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "supplement of the San Francisco Examiner & Chronicle, Sunday,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "October 16, 1966.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "This article deals with the current controversy over",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "the existence or nonexistence of flying saucers or Unidentified",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Flying Objects (UFOs), and quotes Michigan's Congressional",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Representative GERALD FORD as suggesting that Congress look",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "into UFOs; also it announces that the Air Force, which is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "charged with investigating UFOs, has commissioned the Univer-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "sity of Colorado and Physics Professor EDWARD U. CONDON to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "conduct an in-depth study of flying saucers for the next 18",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "months, at an estimated cost of $300,000.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "[unclear]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "The article also points out that since last summer",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "pressure has been mounting for the establishment of an inde-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "pendent, civilian controlled investigative agency to look into",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "the UFO problem.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "Also, for the Bureau's information, there was re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "cently published (first printing June 1966) a book entitled",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "\"Flying Saucers - Serious Business\", Lyle Stuart, Inc.,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "publishers, authored by Frank Edwards. This book is now in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "its third edition and is available in paperback, published",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "by Bantam Books, and it is probably a contributing factor to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "the current controversy.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "In this book author Edwards points out that flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
